{"id": 231998964, "title": "Narendra Modi government 3.0: Full list of ministers taking oath", "text": "BJP leader Narendra Modi took the oath as the Prime Minister of India for the third consecutive term on Sunday. This is historic as no Prime Minister other than Jawaharlal Nehru, the first PM of Independent India, has returned for a third term as the PM. On this historic day, a total of 72 leaders are set to be sworn in to be part of the Modi 3.0 ministry.The new Cabinet will include 30 Cabinet ministers, five Ministers of State with Independent Charge, and 36 Ministers of State.After PM Modi was sworn in, Rajnath Singh, Amit Shah, Nitin Gadkari, and JP Nadda were next to take oaths administered by President Droupadi Murmu.Who gets which ministry in Modi 3.0? Form your 'Dream Cabinet' and win prizes.link__elec{padding:0 0 12px} .link__elec div{margin-bottom:7px;}.link__elec a{color: var(--linkcolor); text-decoration: underline;font-size:18px; line-height:24px; font-weight:600;} Former chief ministers Shivraj Singh Chouhan and Manohar Lal Khattar were inducted into Modi 3.0Nirmala Sitharaman and Dr S Jaishankar, who were part of the previous Narendra Modi-led government, have been inducted into the new ministry as well.Several leaders from the BJP and its NDA allies are set to be inducted as ministers at the swearing-in ceremony at the Rashtrapati Bhavan on Sunday.The leaders who are set to be sworn in for the Union ministry on Sunday include those from the Telugu Desam Party (TDP), JD(U), LJP, Shiv Sena and the NCP.Modi returned as the Prime Minister as the NDA won 293 of the 543 seats in the 2024 Lok Sabha election. The BJP, however, was short of the majority mark in the Lok Sabha on its own, winning 240 seats. The magic number in the Lok Sabha is 272. Published By: Ashutosh AcharyaPublished On: Jun 9, 2024Tune InMust Watch", "summary": "<a href=\"https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/lok-sabha-ministers-modi-government-nda-lok-sabha-portfolios-bjp-2551005-2024-06-09\"> <img align=\"left\" hspace=\"2\" height=\"180\" width=\"305\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/pm-modi-oath-ceremony-090820135-16x9_0.jpeg?VersionId=cCCclT_IYBEMvz0SQoyB8cPXRAwdAbT6\"> </a> Narendra Modi government 3.0: Full list of ministers taking oath", "url": "https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/lok-sabha-ministers-modi-government-nda-lok-sabha-portfolios-bjp-2551005-2024-06-09", "image": "https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/pm-modi-oath-ceremony-090820135-16x9_0.jpeg?VersionId=cCCclT_IYBEMvz0SQoyB8cPXRAwdAbT6?size=1280:720", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 14:02:16", "author": null, "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "in", "sentiment": 0.223}